I loved all 3 seasons and am so looking forward to season 4 when it's offered on Amazon Instant. Laura Linney is at her very very best in this series. Her character and how she brings her to passionate life is phenomenal.  As a cancer survivor myself, she inspires me every time I watch it. She goes thru all the stages of someone given a 'death sentence' diagnosis, but with such love, finesse, courage, humor, beauty, sincerity, etc, it's truly amazing. Since this series, she has become one of my all time favorite actresses...much loved. And the supporting cast!! Not enough can be said abt these real ppl. love this show"
