The best way to describe this film is \"Phantasm\" on drugs. Dave (Chase Williamson) and John (Rob Mayes) are friends who are attempting to save the universe, or at least our planet. They have been chosen to do so by the drug \"Soy Sauce\" which gives them remarkable insight that is more like a bad acid trip.The film is quirky and humorous, but not a side splitter. The dialouge is cute and clever for most of the film, but to the point of ad nauseam.For those who like the \"Scott Pilgrim...\" quick style, check it out.Parental Guide: F-bomb, no sex. Nudity."
